com.camerontec.catalys.core.session

Class MatchingObjectRegistryByConnectionPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.MatchingObjectRegistryByConnectionPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjectRegistryByConnectionPoint

    public class MatchingObjectRegistryByConnectionPoint
extends Object
implements IObjectRegistryByConnectionPoint
    Simple iterative matching registry of (session-related) objects by connection point.

    This registry finds the object registered against a specified connection point by iterating over the set of registered IConnectionPoints and attempting to match each in turn using the specified IConnectionPointMatcher implementation.

    Due to its iterative nature this class has a find time of O(N).
